# GitHub Linguist — keep language stats focused on hand-written source (R + Rust).
# `linguist-generated` / `linguist-vendored` exclude files from the language bar
# (and collapse them in diffs).

# Auto-generated by roxygen2
man/*.Rd             linguist-generated
NAMESPACE            linguist-generated

# Auto-generated by rextendr
R/extendr-wrappers.R linguist-generated
src/Makevars         linguist-generated
src/Makevars.win     linguist-generated

# Cargo lockfile and build output
src/rust/Cargo.lock  linguist-generated
src/rust/target/**   linguist-vendored
src/rust/vendor/**   linguist-vendored
